      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSET OYSTER (1) used the inside draw to advantage last time and hit the ground running with a fast early split, but could manage only the minor money when a 2.25 lengths second at this track over 488m in 27.55. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. One of the leading chances. NOT ATROCIOUS (3) has hit the frame here at the last two runs, most recently finishing second beaten 2.5 lengths (22.71). Looks well placed over the extra ground. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from four attempts. Well-placed to take this out. RAMBO'S SHOUT (7) had to overcome a collision with another runner and could manage only a distant seventh (28.01) in a Free For All over 488m at this track. Key chance on best form. KENTISH LASS (2) is on a run of two minor placings and will be in the mix again.",
